a little bit.

05:15.304 --> 05:16.787
[inhales]

05:16.822 --> 05:18.539
I'm saying $850
takes it today

05:18.574 --> 05:21.275
And gets him his 5%,
and we're out the door.

05:21.309 --> 05:22.343
$775.

05:22.377 --> 05:24.412
I can't go any lower
than $825.

05:24.446 --> 05:27.014
I'm stuck at $775.

05:27.049 --> 05:30.551
$800,
we have a deal today.

05:30.586 --> 05:32.753
The Stash wants me to have
the free t-shirt.

05:32.788 --> 05:34.555
All right.
I'll go $800.

05:34.590 --> 05:36.390
- $800.
- It's a deal.

05:36.425 --> 05:38.226
- Here you go.
- $800 it is.

05:38.260 --> 05:41.779
Don't forget
the Stash's $40.

05:41.830 --> 05:43.531
Well,
why don't you take $50?

05:43.565 --> 05:44.615
You're all right, Vince.
Thank you.

05:44.666 --> 05:45.633
All right.
Thank you.

05:45.667 --> 05:48.236
Make it rain, Vince.
[laughter]

05:48.270 --> 05:49.237
Let's help you get this
into your car.

05:49.271 --> 05:50.238
- Cool. Thank you.
- All right.

05:50.272 --> 05:51.239
- See you later, guys.
- Thank you.

05:51.273 --> 05:52.373
Bye.
Thanks again.

05:52.407 --> 05:53.474
Hey, how's it going?

